  <entry>
    <title>集群故障排查日志-Slurm Nodestate Down</title>
    <url>/year/04/27/%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97-slurm-nodestate-down/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="集群故障排查日志-slurm-nodestate-down"><a href="#集群故障排查日志-slurm-nodestate-down" class="headerlink" title="集群故障排查日志-slurm nodestate down"></a>集群故障排查日志-slurm nodestate down</h1><ul>
<li><p>今天是不知道为什么slurm节点状态变成了down，尝试了几次，在、要注意的点首先是修改slurm登录的账户要是和以前配置slurm的一样。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sinfo <span class="hljs-comment">#发现node 状态是down</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#切换到root</span><br>sudo scontrol update NodeName=node08 State=idle<br>或者<br>sudo scontrol update NodeName=node08 State=RESUME<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>搞定收工</p>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
