  <entry>
    <title>集群故障排查日志—节点无法远程Ssh链接</title>
    <url>/year/04/27/%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E2%80%94%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8Bssh%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="集群故障排查日志—节点无法远程ssh链接"><a href="#集群故障排查日志—节点无法远程ssh链接" class="headerlink" title="集群故障排查日志—节点无法远程ssh链接"></a>集群故障排查日志—节点无法远程ssh链接</h1><ul>
<li><p>这几天突然发现实验室集群无法远程链接了；由于考试没有时间去处理，组里也没有会，放置了半个月，今天去物理机房插上了显示器和键盘，去看看了系统日志</p>
<p>/var/log其中有</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">Feb 25 22:15:38 server kernel: [ 1235.212537] PM: <span class="hljs-built_in">suspend</span> entry (s2idle)<br>Feb 25 22:15:38 server systemd-sleep[1705]: Suspending system...<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>确定了是自动休眠的问题然后就好说了</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">systemctl status sleep.target <span class="hljs-comment">#执行这个命令来确定一下状态</span><br> ● sleep.target - Sleep<span class="hljs-comment">#确认是休眠策略</span><br>    Loaded: loaded (/lib/systemd/system/sleep.target; static; vendor preset: enabled)<br>    Active: inactive (dead)<br>      Docs: man:systemd.special(7)<br> Feb 24 13:18:08 xps systemd[1]: Reached target Sleep.<br> Feb 26 13:29:31 xps systemd[1]: Stopped target Sleep.<br> Feb 26 13:29:57 xps systemd[1]: Reached target Sleep.<br> Feb 26 13:30:19 xps systemd[1]: Stopped target Sleep.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>然后</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sudo systemctl mask sleep.target suspend.target hibernate.target hybrid-sleep.target<br> Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/sleep.target → /dev/null.<br> Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/suspend.target → /dev/null.<br> Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/hibernate.target → /dev/null.<br> Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/hybrid-sleep.target → /dev/null.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>最后</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ systemctl status sleep.target<br>● sleep.target<br>   Loaded: masked (Reason: Unit sleep.target is masked.)<br>   Active: inactive (dead)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>放了两天试了试，确定ok。自动休眠功能已经被关闭，不会出现自动休眠导致远程控制无法访问的情况了。</p>
</li>
<li><p>这个问题我估计是去机房登录物理机导致的，去机房物理机插上键盘显示器调配东西的时候，进入桌面系统了，只有服务器系统才会有不休眠这个设定，所以以后如果要去物理机器调制的时候要注意这个问题。</p>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
